	1. Developer write code --> Pushes to Git
	2. Ci Pipeline builds and tests the code
	3. Artifact is stored in registry 
	4. CD Pipeline deploys to Kubernetes clusters across AWS/Azure/GCP 
	5. IaC provisions all cloud infrastructure 
	6. Monitoring Tracks performance, logs, and alerts
	7. Feedback loop --> Developers fix issues --> push new code --> Cycle repeats. 

